    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock providing exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain its signature communicative handling. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the atmospheric induction note and balanced 50/50 weight distribution offer an undiluted analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
