    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway use. All body panels are straight with consistent gaps, and the factory alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin has been meticulously cared for by a non-smoker; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection completed last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable. It comes with a clean title and a full set of floor mats. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
